sql:
SELECT model_id, MAX(action_date) AS latest_audit_date
FROM model_audits
GROUP BY model_id;

external_knowledge:
- Navigators are users who are active in the system;
- Not leaving footprints in the realm of models means the user has not created any models;
- The frequency of navigation relates to the number of access logs a user has.

sql:
SELECT model_name, version
FROM models
WHERE project_id = 1;

SELECT models.model_name, models.version, model_deployments.status
FROM models
LEFT JOIN model_deployments ON models.model_id = model_deployments.model_id;

SELECT AVG(loss) AS Average_Loss
FROM training_metrics
WHERE model_id = 1 AND epoch > 5;

SELECT MAX(release_date)
FROM model_versions
WHERE model_id = 1;
